items.name: Egg Jeera Rice
items.description: Egg jeera rice is a flavorful and satisfying dish that combines fluffy rice, fragrant cumin seeds [jeera] and scrambled eggs. Cooked to perfection with aromatic spices like cumin and coriander, this dish boasts a tantalizing aroma and a burst of flavors.

items.name: Egg Schezwan Rice [2 Eggs]
items.description: Egg schezwan rice is a delicious fusion dish that combines the bold flavors of Schezwan cuisine with the comfort of fried rice and the protein rich goodness of eggs. This dish typically features cooked rice stir fried with a spicy schezwan sauce, mixed with scrambled or fried eggs.

items.name: Egg Fried Rice [2 Eggs]
items.description: Egg fried rice is a classic and beloved dish that brings together fluffy rice, scrambled eggs and a medley of vegetables, all stir fried to perfection. This versatile dish is known for it is simplicity and deliciousness, making it a favorite comfort food across various cuisines.

items.name: Egg Pulao [3 Eggs]
items.description: Egg pulao is a delightful rice dish infused with aromatic spices and boiled eggs, creating a flavorful and satisfying meal.

items.name: Egg Biryani [2 Eggs]
items.description: Egg biryani is a luxurious and aromatic rice dish that tantalizes the taste buds with its rich flavors and fragrant spices. Basmati rice, infused with a blend of spices such as cumin, cardamom, cinnamon and saffron, forms the flavorful base of this dish.

items.name: Egg Gravy Pulao [2 Eggs]
items.description: Egg gravy pulao is a flavorful and comforting rice dish that combines the richness of a savory gravy with the fluffy texture of rice and the protein punch of boiled eggs. The gravy, typically made with tomatoes, onions, ginger, garlic and a blend of spices, adds depth and richness to the pulao. It coats each grain of rice and egg with its luscious texture and savory taste, creating a harmonious blend of flavors in every bite.

items.name: Egg Bhurji Pulao [2 Eggs]
items.description: Egg bhurji pulao is a delightful fusion dish that combines the flavors of spicy scrambled eggs with fragrant rice, creating a hearty and satisfying meal. Basmati rice serves as the base, cooked with a medley of aromatic spices like cumin, cloves, and cinnamon, lending a rich and flavorful backdrop to the dish.

items.name: Egg Creamy Pulao [2 Eggs]
items.description: Egg creamy pulao is a luxurious and indulgent rice dish that combines the richness of a creamy sauce with the delicate flavor of boiled eggs and aromatic spices. The creamy sauce, a blend of velvety cheese and fresh coriander, lends a luxurious texture and depth of taste to the dish.

items.name: Lehsuni Chutney
items.description: Lehsuni chutney, also known as garlic chutney, is a fiery condiment hailing from Indian cuisine. It is bold flavor comes from a potent combination of garlic cloves, dried red chillies and zesty lemon juice, all expertly blended with aromatic spices like cumin and coriander.

items.name: Tomato Chutney
items.description: Tomato chutney is a tangy and savory condiment that adds a burst of flavor to a variety of dishes. Made primarily from ripe tomatoes, this chutney is seasoned with aromatic spices like mustard seeds, cumin and curry leaves.

items.name: Cheese Chutney
items.description: Cheese chutney is a delectable fusion condiment that combines the creamy richness of cheese with the tangy zest of traditional chutney. Made by blending cheese with a variety of flavorful ingredients such as herbs, spices, cheese chutney offers a delightful balance of savory and sweet notes.
